import React from 'react'
import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Heading,
  Stat,
  StatLabel,
  StatNumber,
  StatHelpText,
  StatArrow,
  StatGroup,
} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const EarningsExpenseInfo = ({
  totalExpenses,
  totalEarnings,
  totalPercentages,
  netProfits,
  changeStatArrow,
  numValuesBgChange
}) => {

  return(
    <Container bg={numValuesBgChange} p={2}>
      <Box>
        <StatGroup>
          <Stat>
            <StatLabel>Expenses</StatLabel>
            <StatNumber>$ {totalExpenses}</StatNumber>
          </Stat>
          <Stat>
            <StatLabel>Earnings</StatLabel>
            <StatNumber>$ {totalEarnings}</StatNumber>
          </Stat>
        </StatGroup>
        <StatGroup>
          <Stat>
            <StatHelpText>
              <Heading size='4xl'>
                <StatLabel>Net</StatLabel>
                <Heading size='2xl'>$ {netProfits}</Heading>
                <StatArrow type={changeStatArrow} />
                {totalPercentages} %
              </Heading>
            </StatHelpText>
          </Stat>
        </StatGroup>
      </Box>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default EarningsExpenseInfo
